13 An Act relating to the Attorney General; defining
terms; establishing a certain pilot program under the
14 Office of the Attorney General; providing purpose;
listing qualifying expenses; stating eligibility
15 requirements; requiring certain application process
and review criteria; requiring certain reports and
16 compliance; authorizing the Office of the Attorney
General to take certain actions; requiring electronic
17 submissions of certain report; authorizing
promulgation of rules; amending Section 1, Chapter
18 376, O.S.L. 2023 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 748.3),
which relates to the Victims of Human Trafficking and
19 Prevention Revolving Fund; expanding the scope of
